00:29:37,368 --> 00:29:39,138
Oh, that's possible.

424
00:29:39,608 --> 00:29:42,809
Civilians can't tell a cop's uniform from a prison guard's.

425
00:29:54,989 --> 00:29:55,989
(Kang In Ho)

426
00:30:01,729 --> 00:30:02,729
Okay.

