443
00:30:50,078 --> 00:30:51,549
You know I'm the killer.

444
00:30:55,249 --> 00:30:56,249
Freeze.

445
00:30:56,949 --> 00:30:58,189
Move and I'll smack you.

446
00:31:01,358 --> 00:31:02,729
