466
00:32:15,328 --> 00:32:16,328
Okay?

467
00:32:16,469 --> 00:32:17,469
Darn you!

468
00:32:19,699 --> 00:32:20,699
Captain Seul.

469
00:32:21,499 --> 00:32:22,499
Thank you.

470
00:32:23,608 --> 00:32:24,838
